@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Policy";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<h2 class="text-center">Policy</h2>

<div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                Electoral System
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                Jordan uses a mixed electoral system combining first-past-the-post and proportional representation. This system aims to balance the representation of individual candidates and political parties, ensuring that both local and national interests are represented in the parliament.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                Quota System
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                Jordan implements a quota system to ensure representation of women and minorities in the parliament. This policy mandates a certain number of seats to be reserved for these groups, promoting diversity and inclusion within the legislative body.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                Voter Registration
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                Citizens must register to vote, and the registration process is overseen by the Independent Election Commission (IEC). The IEC ensures that the voter registration process is accessible, transparent, and secure, allowing eligible voters to participate in the electoral process.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                Independent Election Commission
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                The Independent Election Commission (IEC) is responsible for administering elections and ensuring they are free and fair. The IEC oversees all aspects of the electoral process, from voter registration to the announcement of results, maintaining the integrity of the elections.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                Candidate Eligibility
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                Candidates must meet certain eligibility criteria, including age, nationality, and legal requirements. These criteria ensure that candidates are qualified and capable of representing their constituents effectively in the parliament.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseSix" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                Campaign Regulations
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseSix" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                Campaign activities are regulated to ensure fairness, including spending limits and advertising rules. These regulations prevent undue influence and promote a level playing field for all candidates, ensuring that elections are conducted fairly and transparently.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseSeven" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSeven">
                Polling Stations
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseSeven" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                Polling stations are established across the country to facilitate voter participation. These stations are equipped to handle large numbers of voters efficiently, ensuring that everyone has the opportunity to cast their vote without undue delay or inconvenience.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseEight" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseEight">
                Election Observers
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseEight" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                Domestic and international observers are allowed to monitor elections to ensure transparency. Observers help to maintain the credibility of the electoral process by providing an independent assessment of the conduct of the elections.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseNine" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseNine">
                Vote Counting
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseNine" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                Votes are counted in a transparent manner, and results are announced by the IEC. This process ensures that the outcome of the elections is accurate and reflects the will of the people.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTen" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTen">
                Electoral Disputes
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseTen" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                Mechanisms are in place for addressing electoral disputes and complaints. These mechanisms provide a fair and impartial process for resolving any issues that may arise during the electoral process.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseEleven" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseEleven">
                Media Coverage
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseEleven" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                The media is expected to provide fair and balanced coverage of all candidates and parties. This ensures that voters have access to unbiased information, allowing them to make informed decisions when casting their votes.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwelve" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwelve">
                Voter Education
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseTwelve" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                Initiatives are undertaken to educate voters about their rights and the electoral process. Voter education programs aim to increase voter turnout and ensure that all citizens understand how to participate effectively in the elections.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThirteen" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThirteen">
                Political Party Regulation
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseThirteen" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                Political parties are regulated to ensure they adhere to democratic principles. These regulations promote internal democracy within parties and ensure that they operate transparently and accountably.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFourteen" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFourteen">
                Campaign Finance
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseFourteen" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                There are strict rules regarding campaign finance to prevent undue influence on candidates and parties. These rules include limits on contributions and expenditures, as well as requirements for financial disclosure.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFifteen" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFifteen">
                Electoral Transparency
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseFifteen" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                Measures are taken to ensure the electoral process is transparent and accountable. This includes open access to information, public reporting of election results, and scrutiny by independent bodies.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseSixteen" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSixteen">
                Electronic Voting System
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseSixteen" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                Our website offers an electronic voting system that ensures secure, accessible, and efficient voting for all eligible voters. This system uses advanced encryption and authentication measures to protect voter data and prevent fraud. Voters can cast their ballots online from any location, and the system provides real-time updates and confirmations to ensure transparency and trust in the electoral process. Comprehensive user guides and support are available to assist voters in using the electronic voting system.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
